features: EFFORTLESS CAN OPENING: Cooks Professional electric tin opener does all the hard work for you with its one-touch operation. Just place it on the can, press the button, and watch the automatic can opener effortlessly spin around, leaving you with a perfectly opened can every time.

DESIGNED FOR EVERYONE: Whether you're right-handed or left-handed, the versatile design of our can openers that work caters to all. It's also a game-changer for those with joint or muscle issues. Let us take the strain off your hands and make a can opening a breeze, so you can enjoy your favourite foods.

SAFE AND CLEAN LID REMOVAL: After the tin can opener has completed its job, the built-in magnet gracefully lifts the lid off, leaving you with a smooth, clean edge. It's a simple and safe way to dispose of the lid, ensuring your kitchen stays clean and hazard-free.

CORDLESS CONVENIENCE: The electric can opener is cordless, giving you the freedom to use it wherever you need it most. Whether you're in your kitchen or hosting a picnic, our electric tin openers for arthritis hands are powered by just four AA batteries (not included) for ultimate convenience.

COMPACT AND STYLISH: With sleek dimensions of L18 x W6.9 x H5.7cm, our electric can openers fits seamlessly into any kitchen décor. Plus, rest easy knowing you're buying from a trusted UK supplier, ensuring you receive high-quality can openers backed by our commitment to excellence.
description: Product Description Cooks Professional Automatic Can Opener in Black and Copper If you struggle to open cans or food, then you need the automatic can opener from Cooks Professional. It is easy to use and can get your cans open quickly and safely. Now you can open any tin with a single touch! So simple to operate, just place the automatic can opener on top of the can and, at the press of a single button, it easily opens without leaving sharp edges. When cutting is complete, just lift the can opener and the built-in magnet will effortlessly lift the lid for you.
